What a coincidence.

1459
01:03:46,950 --> 01:03:49,000
When I was in Shanghai,

1460
01:03:49,000 --> 01:03:50,670
GATE M West Coast Dream Center,

1461
01:03:50,670 --> 01:03:51,280
you know that?

1462
01:03:51,520 --> 01:03:51,950
Sure.

1463
01:03:51,950 --> 01:03:53,360
I go rock climbing there often.

1464
01:03:54,360 --> 01:03:55,760
I used to hang out there too.

1465
01:03:55,760 --> 01:03:57,600
We might have crossed paths.

1466
01:03:57,600 --> 01:03:58,320
Really?

1467
01:03:58,320 --> 01:03:58,760
Yeah.

1468
01:04:00,670 --> 01:04:01,470
Put this on.

1469
01:04:03,360 --> 01:04:05,150
It's so cold at night.

1470
01:04:07,000 --> 01:04:08,840
Do yo want to wear my suit?

1471
01:04:08,840 --> 01:04:09,430
It's thicker.

1472
01:04:09,430 --> 01:04:10,800
Sure.

1473
01:04:11,840 --> 01:04:14,190
I'm the type who gets cold easily.

1474
01:04:14,430 --> 01:04:15,360
Here.

1475
01:04:15,360 --> 01:04:15,840
This is thick,

1476
01:04:15,840 --> 01:04:16,600
super thick.

1477
01:04:16,600 --> 01:04:17,190
Let me change.

1478
01:04:17,190 --> 01:04:18,390
Yours looks nicer.

1479
01:04:20,280 --> 01:04:20,870
Feel my hand.

1480
01:04:20,870 --> 01:04:22,430
It's freezing,

1481
01:04:22,430 --> 01:04:23,230
super cold.

1482
01:04:23,230 --> 01:04:23,800
Touch it.

1483
01:04:28,320 --> 01:04:29,190
See?

1484
01:04:29,190 --> 01:04:30,230
Does my hand feel warm to you?

1485
01:04:30,230 --> 01:04:32,190
Yeah, totally the opposite.

1486
01:04:32,230 --> 01:04:33,430
I'm freezing.

1487
01:04:34,630 --> 01:04:35,430
Thanks.

1488
01:04:36,950 --> 01:04:38,000
This is really warm.

1489
01:04:40,280 --> 01:04:41,600
When I was wearing it just now,

1490
01:04:42,470 --> 01:04:44,710
I felt like I'd be drenched in sweat.

1491
01:04:51,840 --> 01:04:53,040
That moment

1492
01:04:53,040 --> 01:04:54,390
when our palms touched,

1493
01:04:54,390 --> 01:04:57,150
I kind of froze,

1494
01:04:57,470 --> 01:04:59,080
a little nervous and shy.

1495
01:04:59,390 --> 01:05:00,910
Her hand was icy.

1496
01:05:00,910 --> 01:05:01,870
Pressed against mine,

1497
01:05:01,870 --> 01:05:03,430
I felt like I was heating up

1498
01:05:03,430 --> 01:05:06,040
like a heating pad.

1499
01:05:18,870 --> 01:05:19,800
Are you afraid of bugs?

1500
01:05:19,800 --> 01:05:20,800
I was when I was little.

1501
01:05:21,230 --> 01:05:23,190
And mosquitoes really love me.

1502
01:05:23,190 --> 01:05:24,230
Have you already been bitten?

1503
01:05:26,040 --> 01:05:27,150
Let me show you.

1504
01:05:28,840 --> 01:05:30,000
Why didn't you say anything?

1505
01:05:30,320 --> 01:05:31,040
Well, look.

1506
01:05:31,040 --> 01:05:32,760
One, two, three, four, five,

1507
01:05:32,760 --> 01:05:33,560
six.

1508
01:05:34,360 --> 01:05:35,520
So many.

1509
01:05:35,520 --> 01:05:37,520
You can really put up with it.

1510
01:05:37,520 --> 01:05:38,390
They even bit me on the face.

1511
01:05:38,390 --> 01:05:39,560
I haven't been bitten

1512
01:05:39,560 --> 01:05:40,080
since I came here.

1513
01:05:40,630 --> 01:05:41,600
Because I'm here with you.

1514
01:05:44,710 --> 01:05:45,390
Really,

1515
01:05:45,390 --> 01:05:47,800
I'm lucky I haven't been bitten,

1516
01:05:47,800 --> 01:05:49,800
or my hands would be
covered with bites by now.

1517
01:05:49,800 --> 01:05:50,630
With me here,

1518
01:05:50,630 --> 01:05:51,320
you won't

1519
01:05:51,320 --> 01:05:53,280
get bitten, trust me.

1520
01:05:56,840 --> 01:05:59,230
If you had to describe yourself

1521
01:05:59,230 --> 01:06:00,390
as something,

1522
01:06:00,390 --> 01:06:01,470
what would it be?

1523
01:06:01,630 --> 01:06:02,320
Me?

1524
01:06:02,320 --> 01:06:02,670
Yes,

1525
01:06:02,670 --> 01:06:03,600
describe yourself.

1526
01:06:06,520 --> 01:06:07,320
A dachshund.

1527
01:06:07,800 --> 01:06:09,390
You're a dachshund?

1528
01:06:11,870 --> 01:06:13,320
You really think you're a dachshund,

1529
01:06:13,320 --> 01:06:14,190
right?

1530
01:06:14,190 --> 01:06:15,710
Or you just like them?

1531
01:06:16,000 --> 01:06:17,800
Because they're hunting dogs,

1532
01:06:17,800 --> 01:06:20,120
fierce outside,

1533
01:06:20,120 --> 01:06:21,190
but super clingy

1534
01:06:21,190 --> 01:06:22,120
and cute

1535
01:06:22,120 --> 01:06:23,040
at home.

1536
01:06:23,040 --> 01:06:24,950
That contrast is real.

1537
01:06:25,190 --> 01:06:26,760
Do you think I'm

1538
01:06:26,760 --> 01:06:28,000
the contrasting type?

1539
01:06:30,870 --> 01:06:32,000
I think so.

1540
01:06:37,230 --> 01:06:38,120
At first,

1541
01:06:38,120 --> 01:06:39,630
it did feel a bit awkward,

1542
01:06:39,630 --> 01:06:40,230
but later I thought

1543
01:06:40,230 --> 01:06:41,000
we ended up

1544
01:06:41,000 --> 01:06:43,470
talking pretty well.

1545
01:06:43,470 --> 01:06:44,430
I originally thought

1546
01:06:44,430 --> 01:06:45,950
he'd be more

1547
01:06:45,950 --> 01:06:47,520
of the cool, reserved type,

1548
01:06:47,520 --> 01:06:50,600
someone who keeps his emotions inward.

1549
01:06:50,800 --> 01:06:51,710
But today I realized

1550
01:06:51,710 --> 01:06:52,840
he actually has

1551
01:06:52,840 --> 01:06:55,040
the happy puppy vibes.

1552
01:06:55,040 --> 01:06:56,670
Total contrast,

1553
01:06:57,040 --> 01:06:58,390
kind of sweet and cute.

1554
01:07:04,390 --> 01:07:05,390
Eat this,

1555
01:07:06,600 --> 01:07:08,600
or you might not get another chance.

1556
01:07:17,000 --> 01:07:17,800
I'll just...

1557
01:07:18,630 --> 01:07:19,390
It's so far,

1558
01:07:20,360 --> 01:07:21,360
really far.

1559
01:07:27,470 --> 01:07:28,840
It's crumbling.

1560
01:07:29,190 --> 01:07:30,600
It's been sitting out too long.

1561
01:07:30,600 --> 01:07:32,710
No, you should've taken a big bite.

1562
01:07:33,910 --> 01:07:35,190
You must eat this.

1563
01:07:36,800 --> 01:07:38,800
My teeth might turn blue.

1564
01:07:39,190 --> 01:07:39,800
Oh, no.

1565
01:07:42,120 --> 01:07:43,630
A little bit.

1566
01:07:44,630 --> 01:07:45,430
Let me see yours.

1567
01:07:47,190 --> 01:07:48,000
So?

1568
01:07:48,190 --> 01:07:49,080
A little bit.

1569
01:07:50,430 --> 01:07:51,360
I think it's this drink.

1570
01:07:51,360 --> 01:07:52,000
Mutated.

1571
01:07:52,710 --> 01:07:54,280
We've mutated.

1572
01:08:07,230 --> 01:08:08,230
Let me go swing for a bit,

1573
01:08:08,230 --> 01:08:09,390
lonely swing.

1574
01:08:18,390 --> 01:08:20,120
I lost the game today,

1575
01:08:20,120 --> 01:08:22,870
so the initiative fell in Lu's hands.

1576
01:08:24,120 --> 01:08:26,040
I've told myself many times

1577
01:08:26,040 --> 01:08:27,830
not to take it to heart.

1578
01:08:27,830 --> 01:08:29,790
You can't stop others
from falling for her.

1579
01:08:30,200 --> 01:08:32,080
I can imagine how romantic

1580
01:08:32,080 --> 01:08:33,950
their date must be.

1581
01:08:38,430 --> 01:08:40,640
Do you like sitting like this,

1582
01:08:40,640 --> 01:08:43,200
watching the waves
crash against the shore?

1583
01:08:43,750 --> 01:08:45,600
I wouldn't want to be alone
at such a moment,

1584
01:08:46,000 --> 01:08:47,720
but being with someone feels nice.

1585
01:08:55,240 --> 01:08:57,200
Do you think I look like Stitch?

1586
01:08:57,870 --> 01:08:59,040
Totally.

1587
01:08:59,040 --> 01:08:59,520
Big Eye.

1588
01:08:59,520 --> 01:09:00,830
So you come off

1589
01:09:00,830 --> 01:09:03,160
as that big-eared type, huh?

1590
01:09:05,720 --> 01:09:06,470
I really regret

1591
01:09:06,470 --> 01:09:08,160
not doing more.

1592
01:09:08,160 --> 01:09:09,870
My heart feels as rough as this sea,

1593
01:09:09,870 --> 01:09:10,790
churning and restless.

1594
01:09:13,040 --> 01:09:14,040
I'm determined

1595
01:09:14,040 --> 01:09:15,430
to go all out

1596
01:09:15,430 --> 01:09:17,160
in the next game

1597
01:09:17,160 --> 01:09:17,950
to fight

1598
01:09:17,950 --> 01:09:19,200
for a date.

1599
01:09:20,270 --> 01:09:22,270
Honestly, I only have a little crush

1600
01:09:22,270 --> 01:09:23,270
on Jiayi.

1601
01:09:23,270 --> 01:09:24,520
If it doesn't work out, I'll leave.

1602
01:09:24,520 --> 01:09:25,040
No big deal.

1603
01:09:25,790 --> 01:09:27,270
Tomorrow, I must win the game.

1604
01:09:27,270 --> 01:09:28,950
I'm the master of my own destiny.

1605
01:09:34,260 --> 01:09:51,220
("Live and Love" Release Schedule)

1606
01:09:51,390 --> 01:09:53,240
(Preview)
Have you been seeing other girls?

1607
01:09:53,310 --> 01:09:53,950
I'll talk

1608
01:09:54,120 --> 01:09:54,830
