1609
01:09:55,830 --> 01:09:57,810
I'm not a proactive person.

1610
01:09:57,810 --> 01:09:58,640
I won't let you get eliminated.

1611
01:09:58,640 --> 01:09:59,470
Don't worry.

1612
01:09:59,600 --> 01:10:00,910
I see he's here too!

1613
01:10:01,310 --> 01:10:02,430
I'm so bored.

1614
01:10:02,600 --> 01:10:04,310
Anyone up for a chat?

1615
01:10:06,240 --> 01:10:07,750
So who's your crush?

1616
01:10:07,910 --> 01:10:08,950
One of you two.

1617
01:10:10,830 --> 01:10:12,430
So today's rule
is that someone has to leave.

1618
01:10:12,560 --> 01:10:15,790
Please pack your luggage
and leave Balance Island.

1619
01:10:16,310 --> 01:10:17,350
He got the lowest votes?

1620
01:10:17,750 --> 01:10:18,430
No one voted for him.

1621
01:10:19,430 --> 01:10:21,040
Tonight, leave fate to decide

1622
01:10:21,040 --> 01:10:22,200
and open the door

1623
01:10:22,200 --> 01:10:23,310
