1624
01:10:23,790 --> 01:10:24,680
Do you feel anything?

1625
01:10:28,200 --> 01:10:30,130
(Pursue love on Balance Island)
Not good with sweet talk.

1626
01:10:30,130 --> 01:10:31,200
(Every Wed. at 12 pm)
That's not what I meant.

1627
01:10:31,200 --> 01:10:31,720
(Recall)
.

1628
01:10:31,780 --> 01:10:32,720
(What's that supposed to mean?)

1629
01:10:32,720 --> 01:10:33,270
Seriously?

1630
01:10:33,270 --> 01:10:34,120
What's wrong with you?

1631
01:10:34,520 --> 01:10:35,870
(I didn't. I'm not.)
I didn't mean it that way.

1632
01:10:35,870 --> 01:10:36,430
If

1633
01:10:36,430 --> 01:10:38,600
you and your buddy liked the same girl,

1634
01:10:38,600 --> 01:10:39,430
would you step aside for him?

1635
01:10:39,860 --> 01:10:41,020
(Confidential)

1636
01:10:41,310 --> 01:10:42,200
Why?

1637
01:10:42,200 --> 01:10:43,470
Because I'm very possessive.

1638
01:10:43,470 --> 01:10:44,870
Maybe I'm just a slow burner.

1639
01:10:44,870 --> 01:10:46,750
You call this cycle very long?

1640
01:10:46,750 --> 01:10:49,000
Others are already married with kids.

1641
01:10:49,520 --> 01:10:51,600
Did you vote sincerely?

1642
01:10:51,790 --> 01:10:52,600
Didn't you?

1643
01:10:52,750 --> 01:10:54,120
I'm a bit overwhelmed.

1644
01:10:54,120 --> 01:10:55,160
I get what you're

1645
01:10:55,160 --> 01:10:55,910
thinking.

1646
01:10:56,390 --> 01:10:57,200
What am I thinking?

1647
01:10:57,200 --> 01:10:58,310
You see right through me, right?

1648
01:10:59,600 --> 01:11:00,680
Don't speak in riddles with me.

1649
01:11:04,040 --> 01:11:05,300
(Watch Live and Love with us)
Let's go, Episode 2!

1650
01:11:05,540 --> 01:11:06,300
(Whoa!)

1651
01:11:06,350 --> 01:11:07,870
(Wolfdog strikes!)
That wolfdog's gonna bite!

1652
01:11:07,870 --> 01:11:09,040
(Masters facing off.)
Masters facing off.

1653
01:11:09,040 --> 01:11:10,000
(on Thu. 12 PM.)
But after the date,

1654
01:11:10,000 --> 01:11:11,310
does someone have to leave?

1655
01:11:11,310 --> 01:11:12,620
(Who will be eliminated?)

1656
01:11:12,900 --> 01:11:13,540
(Insane)

1657
01:11:13,680 --> 01:11:14,790
(Disdain)
No, it's ugly.

1658
01:11:14,790 --> 01:11:15,520
Don't do that.

1659
01:11:15,680 --> 01:11:17,160
What's this supposed to mean?

1660
01:11:17,560 --> 01:11:18,200
I don't get it.

1661
01:11:18,240 --> 01:11:19,950
He doesn't even dare to look!

1662
01:11:19,950 --> 01:11:20,640
Formidable rival.

1663
01:11:21,160 --> 01:11:21,750
Formidable rival.

1664
01:11:22,120 --> 01:11:22,520
Stop talking.

1665
01:11:22,520 --> 01:11:23,510
(Anxious)
You're gonna mess it up.

1666
01:11:23,750 --> 01:11:24,350
No.

1667
01:11:24,350 --> 01:11:25,750
Go, good.

1668
01:11:25,750 --> 01:11:26,470
Well done.

1669
01:11:26,470 --> 01:11:28,160
Someone's falling in love.

1670
01:11:28,160 --> 01:11:29,430
(Shipping them)
Falling in love.

1671
01:11:29,430 --> 01:11:30,790
Showing off like crazy.

1672
01:11:31,680 --> 01:11:32,750
So exciting!

1673
01:11:32,750 --> 01:11:34,200
Subscribe to VIP!

1674
01:11:34,200 --> 01:11:35,420
(Not to be missed)
